      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a glitch. i've been noticing this pattern for months. whenever i start talking about certain topics or get too much attention on my posts, things just start vanishing. it feels way too targeted to be a coincidence. like, wouldn't a company have the tech to \"scrub\" specific traces of a person if they really wanted to? for some kind of security or reputation management reason?",
